data.description: Welcome to this charming 2 Family High Ranch nestled in the heart of Great Kills, Staten Island. This meticulously modern home offers both comfort and convenience with its spacious layout and desirable location. As you step inside, you're greeted by an inviting foyer leading to the main living area upstairs. The UPPER LEVEL features an open concept layout with high ceilings. The living room boasts abundant natural light and adjacent is the well-appointed kitchen, complete with modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar. Down the hall you will find 3 Bedrooms 2 Bath completing the upper level. The LOWER LEVEL features the second apartment, great for an extra income source boasting 2 Bedroom 1 Bath, Kitchen and Living Room.  The FINISHED BASEMENT features a versatile family room perfect for movie nights, Gym station, and Home office. The 4th bathroom and laundry room adds to the convenience of this basement level. Outside, this corner property boasts a beautifully landscaped yard, providing the perfect backdrop for outdoor entertaining with a built-in heated pool size 14x20FT and 8FT deep. A driveway and attached garage offer ample parking space for multiple vehicles. Well maintained and renovated throughout the years. New windows, and Flooring have been replaced with hardwood floors and scratch resistant Vinyl. Updated central air and water system within 1-3 years, Roof done 3 Years ago with solar panels installed for the upper level unit help saving the electricity bill. Built-in speakers throughout the house with a smart light switch setup.  Located in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Great Kills, this home offers easy access to a variety of amenities, including shops, restaurants, parks, and top-rated schools. With its spacious layout, desirable features, and prime location, this high ranch house is ready to welcome you home.
